  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/ca59b3e726274f518deae8f099b9af1a.jpg\" style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《英文天天写》是沪江部落一档写作类节目，其目的在于提升大家的英语写作能力。每期节目主持人都会给出一个话题，积极参加的童鞋还会得到主持人的专业点评哦！想提高英语写作的童鞋千万不要错过哦！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15011/\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0,90,148);\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left: 0px; line-height: 1.8em; margin-right: 5px;\" /></a>去沪江部落订阅本节目！</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>背景介绍：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t色彩－－－赤橙黄绿青蓝紫，其实每一种色彩似一种符号或标志，折射出不同的含义。</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t1. From above description about color, which color would you pick for your favorite one and the reason?<br />\n\t2. In the 2014 new year, which color or indicated meaning you would like to expect?<br />\n\t3. Open discussion: the color of my life</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tThe favor of each color could indicate the personality of an individual. Admittedly, green is my preferred choice among various colors. It is the symbol of new life and hope, and each time when I see the green color the picture of nature shows up in my mind. The <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/photosynthesis\" target=\"_blank\">photosynthesis</a> of green leaves bring the oxygen to the world and absorb carbon dioxide, so green is usually associated with the natural process telling the life magic all the time. Moreover, green is good for eyes and keeps you calm down from <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/stressful\" target=\"_blank\">stressful</a> work or study. It could be a psychological hint of peace. In the new year 2014, I would like to expect the environment to become greener, the world to be with more peace and my life with more colors.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例2：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tBlue is the color I love most of all. It is often associated with nature as it conjures up pictures of ocean and sky in our mind. Also, it also brings us peaceful mind and helps us wind down after work a whole day. From that sense, blue is widely used in room decoration and accessories. Over the past a few years, I have heard a psychology theory to put people in different categories based on colors. It is interesting to know a new perspective on colors and their impact on people.<br />\n\tHowever, I hardly imagine my life in 2014 would only be blue. I would like it to be a little richer and colorful. If the year symbols a <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/palette\" target=\"_blank\">palette</a> of mine, a variety of colors come in different shades would be what I like to see.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15011/item/863985/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a><br />\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p588903/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p588903\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p588794/\">法航447空难纪实：消失的法航447(视频)</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p588772/\">美国女子眼睛嵌心形铂金片挑战极限</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p587662/\">每天要问自己的5个问题 你的答案是什么？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p103560/\">沪江英语资料下载帮助及沪元知识</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p5877